OL,10,GMenopause is a hormone system update
OL,11,Gyou didn’t ask for: no consent, no
OL,12,Guser manual, and no warning label.
OL,13,GOnce installed, it triggers a ripple
OL,14,Geffect across social, mental,
OL,15,Gphysical, and work systems. Subtly
OL,16,Grewriting routines and behaviors
OL,17,Galmost overnight. The system you once
OL,18,Gknew, which used to run seamlessly,
OL,19,Gnow requires debugging, optimization,
OL,20,Gand at times a little creative
